Aqube Smart offers the most comprehensive voice-controlled smart garden experience with Alexa. Control your garden irrigation, lighting and other devices hands free.

Here's a step by step guide:
(1). Download our "Aqube" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you're already registered);
(3). Turn on Aqube Smart devices and connect them with“Aqube”app;
(4). IMPORTANT: You can rename the devices with Aqube Smart App. Echo will get that same name ;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(6). Search the Alexa Skills directory for "Aqube Smart";
(7). Click Enable skill of "Aqube Smart", then input your account username, password and region on the linking page;
(8). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices.

Here are the voice commands Aqube Smart has:

Lights:
Alexa, turn on front garden light
Alexa, turn off front garden light
